            "last_activity_date": 1516977037,
            "creation_date": 1516977037,
            "body": "<p>Easiest way, assuming you don't need to modify the collection through <code>as1<\/code>:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Collection&lt;A&gt; as1 = Collections.unmodifiableCollection(bs);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>If you do need to modify the collection, the only safe thing to do is to copy it:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Collection&lt;A&gt; as1 = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;(bs);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 48463392,
            "question_id": 48463351
        },
        {
            "owner": {
