            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1516977066,
            "creation_date": 1516977066,
            "body": "<p>Additional suggestion :<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public static &lt;A&gt; Collection&lt;A&gt; coerce(final Collection&lt;? extends A&gt; col)\n{\n    return (Collection&lt;A&gt;) col;\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
